                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "ability",
                "ability_type": "interaction",
                "text": "The cobblebone swarm's space is difficult terrain."
            },
            {
                "name": "Settlement Bound",
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "ability",
                "ability_type": "interaction",
                "text": "A typical cobblebone swarm must remain in the settlement where it originated and can travel no farther than 1 mile from it without falling apart into component pieces, reviving if its pieces are returned to this area. Occasionally, cobblebone swarms are bound to a specific building, road, or district, rather than a settlement."
            }
